verses.roman:
jagannātha kara, āra kara bhavanātha
hṛdayānanda sena, āra dāsa bholānātha

synonyms: jagannātha kara—of the name Jagannātha Kara; āra—and; kara bhavanātha—of the name Bhavanātha Kara; hṛdayānanda sena—of the name Hṛdayānanda Sena; āra—and; dāsa bholānātha—of the name Bholānātha dāsa.
translation: Jagannātha Kara, Bhavanātha Kara, Hṛdayānanda Sena and Bholānātha dāsa were the fifteenth, sixteenth, seventeenth and eighteenth branches of Advaita Ācārya.
